ActCanadian Commercial Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of GRANT MITCHELL of Edmonton, Alberta, as a director of the Canadian Commercial Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Wendy L, Morris, whose term has expired.
